JUICER: Chemically augmented super-soldier on borrowed time

The Juicer is a human who has voluntarily connected a drug-delivery
harness to their nervous system, flooding their body with combat
stimulants that grant incredible speed, strength, and reflexes: at the
cost of a shortened lifespan.

Juicers cannot be de-juiced without dying (in most cases), and their
lifespan is roughly five years after conversion. What they gain:
superhuman physical attributes and some of the best combat skills in
the game.

STARTING PACKAGE
  Attribute requirements: PS 9, PE 9.
  Equipment: Juicer drug harness (fitted), light body armor, two
    ranged weapons, vibro-knife, and one year of drug supply.

